Text: James New visit to Houston Cc New will be visiting Houston from Tuesday until Thursday May and would like to meet up with you for an hour during his visit Please could you let me know your availability or get your assistants to get in touch with either myself or Fiona McNaught to arrange a meeting Monday May is a bank holiday in the UK but we will respond to your messages on Tuesday Many thanks for your assistance Clare El lisWood Fiona McNaught x x
